tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
My husband & I have been consulting Dr Kiranmayee since Jul‚Äô20. Dr. Kiranmayee‚Äôs temperament and her preference for natural methods of conceptions are the reasons why we held on to her right till the ‚Äúbeginning‚Äù of a new phase of our lives. Her constant follow-ups, check-ups and scans continued for a few months when my husband was hit with COVID-19 in Nov‚Äô20. Doc advised us to take a break for a few months till he recovers fully. We finally conceived in Apr‚Äô21 and it has been a roller-coaster ever since. Since that time, Dr. Kiranmayee started keeping a personal tab on my well-being and this increased as we progressed through the trimesters. She has been with us every step of the way. From a point where, as a couple, we were thinking that we might have to go for IUI or IVF, to giving birth via the natural process, all of this was possible only because of her expertise.

 

If you‚Äôre a couple who‚Äôs planning a baby and are looking for a trust-worthy doctor, she is the one you need to talk to.
